item.title: Mister Saxobeat - Price Tag
item.description:
Ukulele play along
Price Tag - Jessie J (feat B.o.B)
Using the chords: Am Bb Dm F
Suggested Strum Patterns: D DU U DU (Island strum)
or a slightly harder strum pattern but works much better so worth practicing:
D D X DU UDU X DU
This video is meant for educational purposes.
No copyright infringement intended
